    <item>
      <title>特朗普对“次要关税”的威胁发明了新的贸易武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-threat-of-secondary-tariffs-invents-new-trade-weapon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周一似乎是通过威胁他称其为从委内瑞拉购买石油的国家来扼杀与其他国家的石油贸易的国家，从而发明了一种新的经济股权武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-threat-of-secondary-tariffs-invents-new-trade-weapon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 02:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普内阁消息传递漏洞证实了对欧洲盟友的恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-cabinet-messaging-breach-confirms-fears-of-european-allies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国顶级官员之间的私人文字暴露提供了对本月初对胡塞武装分子的罢工计划的独特见解。这些信息还阐明了他们对欧洲盟友的不屑一顾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-cabinet-messaging-breach-confirms-fears-of-european-allies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 01:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国释放了Mintz的员工，因为它会吸引顶级全球公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/china-frees-mintz-employees-after-two-year-detention-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国释放了五名在2023年被拘留的明兹集团雇员；随着海外投资的投资，明显的努力是赢得外国公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/china-frees-mintz-employees-after-two-year-detention-ft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 01:17:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教育部门的捍卫者起诉以阻止特朗普的大修</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/education-department-defenders-sue-to-block-trump-s-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国两个最大的教师工会和一个著名的民权组织起诉了特朗普政府，以取消教育部门，这增加了越来越多的诉讼，反对总统为改变联邦政府的深远努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/education-department-defenders-sue-to-block-trump-s-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 00:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在特朗普赞扬210亿美元的美国扩张之后，现代汽车跳了起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩国汽车制造商宣布了在美国进行创纪录的210亿美元投资的计划，以减轻唐纳德·特朗普总统对征收大量关税的威胁，这是在美国进行创纪录的210亿美元投资的计划后，现代汽车公司的股价激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国为贸易战争节省了财政权力，因为支出进度滞后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/china-saves-fiscal-power-for-trade-war-as-spending-progress-lags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府似乎并不急于执行其预算，因为北京保留了支出能力来应对较高的美国关税造成的任何损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/china-saves-fiscal-power-for-trade-war-as-spending-progress-lags</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 10:44:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列罢工降低了哈马斯的加沙政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/lethal-israeli-strikes-halve-hamas-top-leadership-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在新的加沙进攻中杀死了哈马斯的两名事实上的内阁成员，旨在消除伊朗支持的激进组织作为军事和执政部队的角色。在20人的论坛中，这给了11人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/lethal-israeli-strikes-halve-hamas-top-leadership-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 22:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
